'''公開哺乳'''是在[[公共空間|公共空間]]或場合以[[母乳|母乳]][[母乳哺育|哺育]][[嬰兒|嬰兒]]，不同的社會文化和法律對此一行為的看法差異甚大。在[[第三世界|第三世界]]、許多西方國家、及一些亞洲國家中，公開哺乳不是爭議之舉，國家法律對此有所保障；而在少數國家、如[[沙烏地阿拉伯|沙烏地阿拉伯]]，明令禁止女性在公共空間暴露[[乳房|乳房]]，即使是為了哺乳也不在允許範圍內。
[[File:El_origen_de_la_Nación.jpg|thumb]]國會議場上哺乳的女性。]]

不過、即使是在公開哺乳合法或可被社會接受的地區，也有一些母親出於顧及觀感、避免受到騷擾或負面評論，而不願意公然暴露乳房哺育嬰兒<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://internationalbreastfeedingjournal.com/content/3/1/11|doi=10.1186/1746-4358-3-11|title=Got milk? Not in public!|pmid=18680578|year=2008|last1=Wolf|first1=J.H.|volume=3|issue=1|page=11|pmc=2518137|journal=International breastfeeding journal|access-date=2016-12-08|archive-date=2015-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151106042421/http://www.internationalbreastfeedingjournal.com/content/3/1/11|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Vance_2005>{{cite journal|author=|title=Breastfeeding Legislation in the United States: A General Overview and Implications for Helping Mothers|journal=LEAVEN|year=2005|volume=41|issue=3|pages=51–4|url=http://www.llli.org/llleaderweb/LV/LVJunJul05p51.html|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070331220518/http://www.llli.org/llleaderweb/LV/LVJunJul05p51.html|archivedate=2007-03-31|access-date=2016-12-08}}</ref><ref name=Jordan_2002>{{cite book |editor-last=Jordan |editor-first=Tim |editor-last2=Pile editor-first2=Steve |title=Social Change|page=233|publisher=Blackwell|year=2002|isbn=9780631233114}}</ref>。據估算，全世界有約 63%的母親曾有在公共場所哺乳的經驗<ref>{{Cite book|title = Breast Feeding With Confidence|last = Cox|first = Sue|publisher = Meadowbrook Press|year = 2002|isbn = 0684040050|location = United States|pages = }}</ref>。也有媒體報導，有婦女在公眾場合哺乳，卻受到其他人的負面評論，或是工作人員制止<ref>{{cite web|title=Places Moms Have Been Shamed For Breastfeeding|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/09/18/dawn-holland-breastfeeding_n_1893681.html#slide=start|publisher=Huffington Post|accessdate=28 September 2015|date=September 18, 2012|archive-date=2015-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150929013228/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/09/18/dawn-holland-breastfeeding_n_1893681.html#slide=start|dead-url=no}}</ref>，此時有些母親會選擇移動到其它地方，而有些母親會譴責那些批評者，並表示如果阻止她這項合法的行為、她將會採取法律行動或發起抗議<ref>{{cite web|title=Dawn Holland, Breastfeeding Mom, Asked To Nurse In Applebee's Bathroom|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/09/18/dawn-holland-breastfeeding_n_1893681.html|publisher=Huffington Post|accessdate=28 September 2015|date=September 18, 2012|archive-date=2015-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150929013228/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/09/18/dawn-holland-breastfeeding_n_1893681.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，抗議包括公開[[杯葛|杯葛]]該企業、組織哺乳[[快閃族|快閃族]]等等。而某些企業也對此道歉並承諾會重新訓練旗下員工。

== 各地的法律及態度 ==
=== 非洲 ===
[[File:Nursing_area_sign.png|thumb]]是用來標示可哺乳場域的標誌。]]
母親通常會用一塊長長的布把嬰兒揹在後面，只要轉到前面就能進行哺乳。母親在哺乳時不會特地遮掩<ref name="Breastfeeding in public">{{cite web | url=http://www.007b.com/public-breastfeeding-world.php | title=Breastfeeding in public around the world | publisher=007 Breasts | accessdate=15 October 2014 | archive-date=2014-10-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141008045416/http://www.007b.com/public-breastfeeding-world.php | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 亞洲 ===
==== 中國大陸 ====
在[[上海|上海]]，公開哺乳被一些人認為尷尬，但也被許多人接受，且已經有在公眾場所設置哺乳室的呼籲<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/china/2007-01/27/content_794272.htm|title=Congress to consider privacy issue|work=chinadaily.com.cn|accessdate=2016-12-08|archive-date=2009-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090307105647/http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/china/2007-01/27/content_794272.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/opinion/2007-01/29/content_795228.htm|title=Breastfeeding in public|work=chinadaily.com.cn|accessdate=2016-12-08|archive-date=2009-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090620071708/http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/opinion/2007-01/29/content_795228.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==== 馬來西亞 ====
公開哺乳在馬來西亞是可被接受的。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.babycenter.com.my/baby/breastfeeding/tips-for-breastfeeding-inpublic/|title=BabyCenter mums’ tips for breastfeeding in public|location=Malaysia|work=BabyCenter|accessdate=2016-12-08|archive-date=2012-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120527144646/http://www.babycenter.com.my/baby/breastfeeding/tips-for-breastfeeding-inpublic/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==== 菲律賓 ====
在菲律賓，有許多關於哺乳的法律。如2009年的《擴大母乳餵養促進法》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lawphil.net/statutes/repacts/ra2010/ra_10028_2010.html|title=R.A. No. 10028|work=lawphil.net|accessdate=2016-12-08|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305175720/http://lawphil.net/statutes/repacts/ra2010/ra_10028_2010.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>和行政命令第51號《菲律賓哺乳法》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lawphil.net/executive/execord/eo1986/eo_51_1986.html|title=E.O. No. 51|work=lawphil.net|accessdate=2016-12-08|archive-date=2011-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111028220002/http://www.lawphil.net/executive/execord/eo1986/eo_51_1986.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 都保障女性在公眾場所哺乳的權利。雇主必須允許處於哺乳期的母親哺乳或是將母乳擠出儲存。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chroniclesofanursingmom.com/2013/03/more-on-legal-rights-of-breastfeeding.html|title=Chronicles of a Nursing Mom: More on the Legal Rights of Breastfeeding and Working Women|work=chroniclesofanursingmom.com|accessdate=2016-12-08|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402132748/http://www.chroniclesofanursingmom.com/2013/03/more-on-legal-rights-of-breastfeeding.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 在辦公室、商場、政府機關和學校一類的公眾場合，需要設置哺乳室，母親可以在裡面哺乳。此外、奶製品法禁止對適用於兩歲以下嬰兒的嬰兒食品或奶瓶進行廣告。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.pcw.gov.ph/law/executive-order-no-51# |title=Philippine Commission on Women Executive Order No. 51 |access-date=2016-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161213114954/http://www.pcw.gov.ph/law/executive-order-no-51 |archive-date=2016-12-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

==== 沙烏地阿拉伯 ====
沙烏地阿拉伯禁止婦女當眾裸露臉與手以外的身體部位，因此婦女們在哺乳時必須謹慎小心。<ref>{{cite book|last=Riordan|first=Jan|title=Breastfeeding and Human Lactation|pages=718–719|isbn=0-7637-4585-5|year=2005|chapter=The Cultural Context of Breastfeeding|chapterurl=https://books.google.com/books?id=-XhKfbW8ig8C&pg=PA718&dq=%22public+breastfeeding%22&lr=&ei=ciZfSfyiNoPAlQTF4tj7BQ#PPA715,M1|publisher=Jones and Bartlett|location=Sudbury, Mass.|access-date=2016-12-08|archive-date=2020-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201104202357/https://books.google.com/books?id=-XhKfbW8ig8C&pg=PA718&dq=%22public+breastfeeding%22&lr=&ei=ciZfSfyiNoPAlQTF4tj7BQ#PPA715,M1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=zm2b44hVKjoC&pg=PT150&dq=%22+breastfeeding+in+public%22+saudi+arabia&ei=iSlfSZz3PJWckASUvfzqCA|title=Dimensions of Human Behavior|work=google.com}}</ref>

==== 台灣 ====
{{Wikisource|公共場所母乳哺育條例}}
《[[性別工作平等法|性別工作平等法]]》第18條保障了受雇婦女在非休息時間的哺乳或集乳權利，而第23條則規定了受雇者滿一百人以上的雇主必須提供{{le|哺集乳室|Lactation room}}，且需提供托兒設施或措施<ref>[http://law.moj.gov.tw/LawClass/LawAll.aspx?PCode=N0030014 性別工作平等法] {{Wayback|url=http://law.moj.gov.tw/LawClass/LawAll.aspx?PCode=N0030014 |date=20201123203751 }}，全國法規資料庫。</ref>。2010年通過的《公共場所母乳哺育條例》則更明確地保障了女性公開哺乳的權利，當中提到公眾設施對哺集乳室的規定，也提到政府機關必須倡導母乳哺育，而阻止或禁止女性公開哺乳者則可處新臺幣六千元以上三萬元以下罰鍰<ref>[http://law.moj.gov.tw/LawClass/LawAll.aspx?PCode=L0070036 公共場所母乳哺育條例] {{Wayback|url=http://law.moj.gov.tw/LawClass/LawAll.aspx?PCode=L0070036 |date=20201117092430 }}，全國法規資料庫。</ref>。

2012年7月18日，一位母親在[[國立故宮博物院|國立故宮博物院]]哺乳遭工作人員勸離，引發大量台灣網友不滿<ref>{{cite web |url=http://59.151.17.12/html/womenofchina/report/143187-1.htm |title=Taipei Museum Faces Investigation for Evicting Breastfeeding Mother |author=Liu Yunting |date=July 23, 2012 |work=Translated from Shenzhen Evening News |publisher=All-China Women's Federation |accessdate=August 14, 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180126185038/http://59.151.17.12/html/womenofchina/report/143187-1.htm |archive-date=2018-01-26 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，故宮也被開罰新台幣六千元。

=== 歐洲 ===
==== 德國 ====
雖然公開哺乳廣泛地被接受，但德國並沒有關於哺乳的專法。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://eltern.t-online.de/stillen-in-der-oeffentlichkeit-normal-oder-obszoen-/id_20622508/index |title=Breastfeeding in Public, ''T-Online'' 18 November 2009 Language: German |accessdate=2016-12-08 |archive-date=2011-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111010032553/http://eltern.t-online.de/stillen-in-der-oeffentlichkeit-normal-oder-obszoen-/id_20622508/index |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[德國基本法|德國基本法]]第6條第2款規定「撫養與教育子女是父母的自然權利」，第4款規定「每一母親均有享受社會保護和照顧的權利。」。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.iuscomp.org/gla/statutes/GG.htm#6 |title=Art 6 GG - German Basic Law |accessdate=2016-12-08 |archive-date=2017-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170323071619/http://www.iuscomp.org/gla/statutes/GG.htm#6 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==== 冰島 ====
公開哺乳是普遍且沒有爭議的行為。<ref>{{cite web|title=Taking care of children in Iceland|url=http://nordicmum.com/taking-care-of-children-in-iceland/|website=www.nordicmum.com|accessdate=20 November 2016|archive-date=2016-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161010004640/http://nordicmum.com/taking-care-of-children-in-iceland/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==== 荷蘭 ====
在荷蘭，沒有關於公開哺乳的專法，公開哺乳是廣泛被社會接受的。荷蘭法律規定，雇主有義務提供嬰兒出生未滿九個月的女性員工合適的哺乳室，且哺育或使用擠乳器的時間可達工時的四分之一，在嬰兒出生滿九個月後，雇主也必須要提供適合哺乳的環境和時間。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.borstvoeding.com/borstbaan/wet.html|title=Borstvoeding.com: kenniscentrum voor borstvoeding - artikelen- Borst & Baan - Borst & Baan en de wet|work=borstvoeding.com|accessdate=2016-12-08|archive-date=2013-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130809055356/http://www.borstvoeding.com/borstbaan/wet.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

==== 挪威 ====
公開哺乳在挪威是非常普遍的行為，以母乳哺嬰育兒的觀念也如同常識。<ref>[http://old.ltn.com.tw/2003/new/oct/22/today-int3.htm 挪威女性哺乳率 領先全球] {{Wayback|url=http://old.ltn.com.tw/2003/new/oct/22/today-int3.htm |date=20180929102456 }}自由時報。</ref>

==== 英國 ====
根據[[英國國會|英國國會]]在1975年通過的性別歧視法案，公開哺乳是受到保障的，如果嬰兒未滿六個月，在2008年通過的修正案對其母親有額外的保障。這項保障被2010年通過的平等法案所取代。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/85008/business-quickstart.pdf |title=Equality Act 2010: What do I need to know?<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2016-12-08 |archive-date=2013-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131231001143/https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/85008/business-quickstart.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=EqualityAct_2010>{{cite web | title=Equality Act 2010 | publisher=Office of Public Sector Information | date=2010-04-08 | url=http://www.statutelaw.gov.uk/content.aspx?activeTextDocId=3698792 | accessdate=2010-08-27 | archive-date=2012-12-24 | archive-url=https://archive.is/20121224171341/http://www.statutelaw.gov.uk/content.aspx?activeTextDocId=3698792 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

2004年{{le|英國衛生部|Department of Health (United Kingdom)}}調查發現：84%的人可以接受公開哺乳，但有67%的母親擔心社會觀感而反對公開哺乳。<ref name=UK-DOH_2004>{{cite press release | title = Myths stop women giving babies the best start in life | publisher = UK Department of Health | date = 2004-05-10 | url = http://www.dh.gov.uk/PublicationsAndStatistics/PressReleases/PressReleasesNotices/fs/en?CONTENT_ID=4081944&chk=b8wDo%2B | accessdate = 2007-02-16 | archive-date = 2004-05-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20040519035042/http://www.dh.gov.uk/PublicationsAndStatistics/PressReleases/PressReleasesNotices/fs/en?CONTENT_ID=4081944&chk=b8wDo%2B | dead-url = no }}</ref> 為了消除這項疑慮，[[蘇格蘭議會|蘇格蘭議會]]在2005年通過了保障女性在公眾場合哺乳的法律，<ref name=ScotlandBill_2005>{{cite web | title=Breastfeeding etc. (Scotland) Act 2005 | publisher=Queen's Printer for Scotland | date=2005-02-10 | url=http://www.opsi.gov.uk/legislation/scotland/acts2005/20050001.htm | accessdate=2007-01-24 | archive-date=2012-05-08 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67VNVmZky?url=http://www.legislation.gov.uk/asp/2005/1/contents | dead-url=no }}</ref> 該法對在公眾場所阻止女性哺乳者會處以高達2500英鎊的罰款。<ref name=BBC_2004>{{cite news | title=MSPs approve breastfeeding move | date=2004-09-23 | publisher=BBC News | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/scotland/3682824.stm | accessdate=2007-01-24 | archive-date=2006-06-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060613201452/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/scotland/3682824.stm | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.scotland.gov.uk/Publications/2006/07/04152607/1|title=The Breastfeeding etc. (Scotland) Act 2005: Advice for Employers|work=scotland.gov.uk|accessdate=2016-12-08|archive-date=2013-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131231001038/http://www.scotland.gov.uk/Publications/2006/07/04152607/1|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 北美洲 ===
==== 加拿大 ====
[[加拿大權利與自由憲章|加拿大權利與自由憲章]]第28條明定在法律上兩性平等，沒有明確提到哺乳。加拿大哺育嬰兒行動聯盟是一個非政府組織，旨在促進母乳餵養、嬰兒保健及孕產婦福利。<ref>{{cite web|last=Sterken|first=Elisabeth|title=INFACT Canada|url=http://infactcanada.ca/|accessdate=12 March 2014|archive-date=2014-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140104214335/http://infactcanada.ca/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===== 因紐特人 =====
[[因紐特人|因紐特人]]的母乳哺育率極低，遠低於加拿大人的平均數值。根據2006年的統計報告，24%的因紐特兒童從未被母乳餵養過。當地為了增加因紐特人了解以母乳哺育的益處，特地制定了計劃。<ref>{{cite book|last=Asuri|first=Sirisha|title=Early Inuit child health in Canada. Report 2, Breastfeeding among Inuit in Canada|year=2011|publisher=Inuit Tapiriit Kanatami|location=Ottawa|pages=5–8}}</ref>

==== 美國 ====
2006年，育兒雜誌《Babytalk》8月號的封面是一幅哺乳照片，即使沒有露出乳頭，依然遭到大量讀者投訴，許多投訴的內容——當中有許多是為人母親——認為該封面「粗鄙噁心」，在後續的調查中顯示，四千名讀者中有四分之一的人認為封面是負面的。《Babytalk》的編輯Susan Kane對此評論：「有個巨大的禁慾傾向籠罩著美國」。在2004年的一項調查中，3719名受訪者中有43%的人認為女性有公開哺乳的權利。<ref name="auto">{{cite news|title=Eyeful of breast-feeding mom sparks outrage|url=http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/14065706/ns/health-womens_health/t/eyeful-breast-feeding-mom-sparks-outrage/|accessdate=25 November 2011|date=2006-07-27|agency=Associated Press|archive-date=2011-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111216101356/http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/14065706/ns/health-womens_health/t/eyeful-breast-feeding-mom-sparks-outrage/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

美國關於哺乳的法律因州而異，聯邦政府有一個效力有限的允許母乳餵養的修正案，該修正案在1999年9月29日成為法律。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://thomas.loc.gov/cgi-bin/bdquery/z?d106:HZ00295: |title=Breastfeeding Amendment |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150504153044/http://thomas.loc.gov/cgi-bin/bdquery/z?d106:HZ00295: |archivedate=2015-05-04 |accessdate=2016-12-08 }}</ref>它規定，州政府不得禁止婦女在屬於聯邦政府的建物內哺乳，同時規定婦女可以在屬於聯邦政府的建築物內的任何地點哺乳。
<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.glin.gov/download.action?fulltextId=170184&documentId=67358&glinID=67358|title=Treasury and General Government Appropriations Act, 2000|accessdate=13 July 2012}}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }} section 647.</ref>

[[患者保護與平價醫療法案|患者保護與平價醫療法案]]第4207條修正了{{le|公平勞動基準法|Fair Labor Standards Act}}，如果員工的孩子年齡小於一歲，雇主必須提供合理的休息時間和廁所以外的私人空間，以便母親哺育孩子<ref name=ppaca>[http://frwebgate.access.gpo.gov/cgi-bin/getdoc.cgi?dbname=111_cong_bills&docid=f:h3590enr.txt.pdf Patient Protection and Affordable Care Act] {{Wayback|url=http://frwebgate.access.gpo.gov/cgi-bin/getdoc.cgi?dbname=111_cong_bills&docid=f:h3590enr.txt.pdf |date=20110706032624 }}. ''Government Printing Office''. Page 459.</ref>，該時段不予支薪<ref name=ppaca/>。不過若員工少於五十人，雇主可以不必遵守以免造成財務和空間資源不足的困擾。<ref>{{cite news |title=Breastfeeding rooms hidden in health care law |work=CNN |date=April 9, 2010 |first=Elizabeth |last=Landau |url=http://www.cnn.com/2010/HEALTH/04/09/breast.feeding.society/index.html?hpt=C2 |accessdate=2016-12-08 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924150714/http://www.cnn.com/2010/HEALTH/04/09/breast.feeding.society/index.html?hpt=C2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

截至2015年9月，49個州、[[華盛頓哥倫比亞特區|哥倫比亞特區]]和[[美屬維京群島|維京群島]]已經通過立法，明令保障公開哺乳的權利，[[愛達荷州|愛達荷州]]和[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]則是例外。此外，29個州、哥倫比亞特區和維京群島也賦予公開哺乳的婦女對公然猥褻和[[不雅暴露|不雅暴露]]起訴的豁免權。<ref name="state legislatures">{{cite web|title=BREASTFEEDING STATE LAWS|url=http://www.ncsl.org/research/health/breastfeeding-state-laws.aspx|website=National Conference of State Legislatures|publisher=National Conference of State Legislatures|accessdate=3 December 2015|date=2 September 2015|archive-date=2015-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151130120629/http://www.ncsl.org/research/health/breastfeeding-state-laws.aspx|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

=== 大洋洲 ===
==== 澳大利亞 ====
澳大利亞國會在1984年通過了相關法案，明令禁止對婦女的哺乳行為有所歧視。<ref>''Sex Discrimination Act 1984'', [http://www.austlii.edu.au/au/legis/cth/consol_act/sda1984209/s7aa.html s.7AA] {{Wayback|url=http://www.austlii.edu.au/au/legis/cth/consol_act/sda1984209/s7aa.html |date=20150322113138 }}.</ref> 此法案適用於公眾場所與半公眾場所。<ref name="breastfeeding.asn.au">{{cite web|url=https://www.breastfeeding.asn.au/bf-info/breastfeeding-and-law/legalright|title=Breastfeeding in public - your legal rights|work=Australian Breastfeeding Association|accessdate=2016-12-08|archive-date=2018-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181112101555/https://www.breastfeeding.asn.au/bf-info/breastfeeding-and-law/legalright|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==== 紐西蘭 ====
公開哺乳非常普遍，其普遍的程度甚至會讓公開以奶瓶餵養嬰兒的婦女感到不舒服。此外、許多購物中心內都提供了「親子房」以讓母親可以更舒適地哺育孩子。<ref name="Breastfeeding in public"/>

=== 南美洲 ===
在南美洲的大部分地區，公開哺乳是很正常的，用奶瓶哺育嬰兒反而較不普遍。<ref name="Breastfeeding in public"/>

